**Lab Assistant** | Solo Miscellaneous - Disease Team
__Basics__ 
The Lab Assistant wins with the evil scientists and joins a channel with them to communicate securely.
__Details__
The Lab Assistant does not have any special abilities. If somebody tries to copy an evil scientist a Lab Assistant is created instead. 
The Lab Assistant can be a carrier of the disease but once they become contaminated they don't die and instead stay contagious for the rest of the game.
The evil scientist may not directly contaminate the Lab Assistant using one of their vials.
